OL,6,FThe funeral business at the centre of
OL,7,Fa police investigation into the care
OL,8,Fof bodies has council debts of more
OL,9,Fthan #50,000.
OL,11,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors,
OL,12,Fbased in Hull, owes Hull City Council
OL,13,F#51,508.46 and East Riding Council
OL,14,F#2,000.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Hull authority
OL,17,Fsaid it was looking into how to get
OL,18,Fthe money back.
