OL,6,FIn a statement they said: "The debt in
OL,7,Fquestion relates to unpaid fees and
OL,8,Fcharges, including cremation fees. The
OL,9,Fdebt totals #51,508.46. We are
OL,10,Fcurrently exploring options to recoup
OL,11,Fany monies owed to the authority."
OL,13,FThe news emerged before a meeting of
OL,14,FHull council on Thursday, during which
OL,15,Fit was revealed that around 2,000
OL,16,Fcalls have been made to a special
OL,17,Fhotline set up by police since their
OL,18,Finvestigation began on Wednesday 6
OL,19,FMarch.
