OL,6,FEnquiries started after concerns were
OL,7,Fraised about the "care of the
OL,8,Fdeceased".
OL,10,FLast week, Humberside Police said 35
OL,11,Fbodies had been removed from premises
OL,12,Fbelonging to Legacy in Hessle Road,
OL,13,Fwest Hull.
OL,15,Fare on bail.
OL,17,FThis week both Hull and East Riding
OL,18,Fcouncils announced in the wake of the
OL,19,Finvestigation.
