OL,6,FSpeaking during Thursday's full
OL,7,Fcouncil meeting, council leader Mike
OL,8,FRoss said the impact on people in Hull
OL,9,Fwould be felt for months, or even
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FHe said the council was working with
OL,13,Fother organisations, including the
OL,14,Fhealth service, to provide counselling
OL,15,Fand mental health support to those
OL,16,Faffected.
