OL,6,FCllr Ross said: "Our sympathy is with
OL,7,Fall those caught up in these events,
OL,8,Fthe true magnitude of this is yet to
OL,9,Fcome to light. The passing of a loved
OL,10,Fone is a terrible time whenever it
OL,11,Fhappens, for families to be affected
OL,12,Fby what's happened here is doubly
OL,13,Ftragic.
OL,15,F"For every deceased individual there
OL,16,Fwill be eight or nine people affected.
OL,17,FThe police have received over a couple
OL,18,Fof thousand calls to the dedicated
OL,19,Fhelpline number.
