OL,6,F"Many people will have questions and
OL,7,Fsome of those questions will go
OL,8,Funanswered. This will be one of, if
OL,9,Fnot the, most harrowing matters
OL,10,Fcouncil and other staff have had to
OL,11,Fdeal with in their professional lives.
OL,12,FThe impact will be felt for many
OL,13,Fmonths and even years to come."
OL,15,FCouncillors passed an emergency
OL,16,Fmotion, brought by Cllr Daren Hale
OL,17,Fcalling for the funeral industry to be
OL,18,Fregulated.
